title: In the Old Church Tower
creator: Thomas Bailey Aldrich
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox volunteers bring you 14 recordings of In the Old Church Tower by Thomas Bailey Aldrich. This was the Weekly Poetry project for October 14, 2012. "Very lovely poem." - Caprisha Page "This seems like a nice nostalgic poem of a small town landmark." - Leonard Wilson For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. Download M4B (10MB)
subject: librivox; literature; audiobook; poetry; memoirs; philosophy; religion
